        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_3369558630334399659.png",
                "id": "talent88133",
                "key": "Thunderous Wingslash",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Thunderous Wingslash"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span> to the opposing character affected by <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lightning Rod</span>. (If there are no eligible opposing characters, deals DMG to the active character instead)</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Lightning Rod</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the attached character takes DMG from Thunder Manifestation or its summons:</span> Remove this state, cause this DMG instance to increase by 1.<br>(Only one of this status can exist on the field at once. Some of Thunder Manifestation's skills will target the character to which this is attached.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/8e1f1486bab5fc117e480c06e923634b_2251450479513478347.png",
                "id": "talent98429",
                "key": "Strifeful Lightning",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Strifeful Lightning"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>, summons 1 <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Thundering Shackles</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/71e8c31afa5e7b779c1b2604bccc7b1e_2718372305306701845.png",
                "id": "talent25944",
                "key": "Thundering Shackles",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Thundering Shackles"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When battle begins, create a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lightning Strike Probe</span> on the opponent's side of the field.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Lightning Strike Probe</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After a character on whose side of the field this card is on uses a Skill:</span> Attach <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lightning Rod</span> to the active character on that side. (Once per Round)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/7fcdf904a4d1623ab0a882884eb4c2e2_4965727222313995069.png",
                "id": "talent35257",
                "key": "Lightning Probe",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Lightning Probe"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span> to the opposing character affected by <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lightning Rod</span>. (If there are no eligible opposing characters, deals DMG to the active character instead)<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">U</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">sage(s): 1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Lightning Rod</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the attached character takes DMG from Thunder Manifestation or its summons:</span> Remove this state, cause this DMG instance to increase by 1.<br>(Only one of this status can exist on the field at once. Some of Thunder Manifestation's skills will target the character to which this is attached.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1569256823992316171.png",
                "id": "talent79683",
                "key": "Thundering Shackles",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/8fe464d5ca7b4e1ea4b17f6e7f5161fb_4651742788093512874.png",
                "title": "Thundering Shackles"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_2174199264508130623.png",
                "id": "talent8052",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2023/12/17/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_4462855239197037880.png",
