                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Meow...\" \"Guests at the tavern sometimes tell us stories too. I remember one particular legend from Inazuma well — it was said that on a certain island shrouded in dark clouds and lightning, there were times when a shrill sound would carry on the air...\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: \"Thunder Manifestation\" is immune to Frozen, Stun, and Petrification, and starts with \"Elemental Lifeform: Electro\" attached to it. It will also deal +1 DMG to characters affected by \"Lightning Rod.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
