                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Tavern Challenge: Serious Showdown - Howl of the Thunder Manifestation",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Meow...\" \"It seems that none know what that purple being has been through, but its long, drawn-out cry seems to exude an air of... sorry?\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: \"Thunder Manifestation\" is immune to Frozen, Stun, and Petrification, and starts with \"Elemental Lifeform: Electro\" attached to it. It will also deal +1 DMG to characters affected by \"Lightning Rod.\"",
                      "type": "text"
